Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.56,0:00:03.69,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Whodunit?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.69,0:00:06.16,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Who commited the crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.16,0:00:12.98,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10\fad(0,200)}Basically, a mystery work where emphasis is placed upon finding a criminal through logic and reasoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.74,0:00:18.36,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Today, let's playback "The Night Baron Murder Case (Suspicion Part),"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.36,0:00:21.50,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}where there are many suspects!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.51,0:00:25.37,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Love lasts forever, riddles are puzzling...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.37,0:00:27.79,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}...and Saturday nights are for mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.79,0:00:30.13,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Today's star is Ran-{\i1}néechan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:32.45,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Between fighting and worrying,\Nshe plays a major part!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.45,0:00:34.08,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.08,0:00:36.08,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.08,0:00:37.91,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.63,0:22:50.30,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(200,0)}I'll shine on you the light you once shone upon me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.30,0:22:59.60,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6}as I offer my endless love to you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.61,0:23:11.49,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6}Even if those times seem to have shattered,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:17.54,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6}you were right there next to me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.54,0:23:24.63,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6}All you had to say was "It'll be okay"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.63,0:23:32.93,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6}and I'd be back on my feet, time after time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.93,0:23:40.14,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6}I'll shine on you the light you once shone upon me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.14,0:23:44.15,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6}In your voice and eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.15,0:23:47.98,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6}I can feel a gentle warmth, like a burning lamp
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.98,0:23:54.49,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6}and I'll never let it burn out again...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.49,0:24:02.50,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(0,300)}So I dedicate to you this eternal vow
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.78,0:24:38.91,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10\i1}kaze
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.78,0:24:38.91,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Next Conan's Hint: The wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.91,0:24:44.39,o{\rHonorifics - o-tanoshimi}-tan{\r}oshimi,,0000,0000,0000,,Look forward to the next episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.91,0:24:41.08,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0110,,{\be10\an8}Conan{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-kun{\r\be10}, do you have a fever? ({\i1}kaze{\i0} = cold)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.08,0:24:42.33,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0110,,{\be10\an8}I meant the wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.08,0:24:42.33,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0110,,{\be10\i1}uindo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.33,0:24:44.39,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0110,,{\be10\an8}Oh, that's a window, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.34,0:02:22.24,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Ran, the old man, and I attended\Nthe Izu Mystery Tour
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:28.25,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}in place of Dr. Agasa, his friend,\Nand that friend's granddaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:33.63,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The anonymous tour organiser\Nwould play the Night Baron
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:36.05,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and cause an incident during the tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:41.73,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Whoever determines the organiser's\Nidentity gets to stay for free
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.73,0:02:46.60,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and receives floppy disks\Ncontaining a certain program.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:49.52,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The attendees keep\Neach other in check...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:53.13,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The Night Baron pushed me off\Na balcony when I was all alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:56.42,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}...but I fell into a pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:03:00.64,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Was this a warning? Or just part of the game?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:04.24,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}And then it happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.85,0:03:08.19,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The Night Baron plummeted\Nonto a bronze statue!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:18.34,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Izu Princess Hotel
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:20.30,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A person wearing a mask!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:32.14,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Like I thought, it {\i1}was{\i0} the Night Baron who fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:36.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.19,0:03:40.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:41.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:47.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Don't you live\Nwith Detective Mouri?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.49,0:03:49.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! You know better!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:52.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.20,0:03:53.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it isn't Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.79,0:03:55.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:59.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you Yokomizo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} from the\NSaitama police department?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:00.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:02.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:05.99,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Yokomizo\NTransferred to Shizuoka Police Department
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:06.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0035,,I transferred to Shizuoka last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.25,0:04:08.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:09.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:13.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ebara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:16.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know him, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:17.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:20.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was on the same\NMystery Tour as us...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:22.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystery Tour!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:26.10,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10\fad(0,200)}He only has one glove on...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.84,0:04:32.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:36.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So the goal is to figure out who\Nthe organiser and Night Baron is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.61,0:04:41.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means the organiser\Nwas Ebara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:47.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A suicide? An accident? Or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:51.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, where is Detective Mouri?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:52.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.46,0:04:54.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the pub on the 2nd floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.53,0:04:55.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:58.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamijō{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:05:01.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's go talk to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.21,0:05:02.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Come on, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.67,0:05:03.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:04.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:09.37,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10\fad(200,200)}Tears?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:15.71,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Hotel 2F\NPub "Emerald"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:19.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.53,0:05:24.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What!? Ebara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} fell off\Ndressed as the Night Baron!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:30.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, according to eyewitnesses,\Nhe fell at precisely 10 PM!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:32.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.45,0:05:34.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your breath...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:37.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,10 PM, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.88,0:05:38.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.63,0:05:41.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! It's this late already!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:46.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, did you check Room 2101,\Nwhere he was staying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:50.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We tried to, but we\Ncouldn't get inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:58.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A security lock on the inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:05:59.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:12.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! We're in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:17.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are clothes here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:20.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the ones\Nhe was wearing today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.77,0:06:23.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He even left his room key here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:28.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,\Nhe {\i1}was{\i} pretty drunk...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:32.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The window's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:35.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's a veranda outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:43.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It would appear this\Nis where he fell from.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.11,0:06:45.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Careful, Detective Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:49.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This was just a simple accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:51.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,An accident!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:55.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt about it.\NThere's a glove in the railing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:56.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:02.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably tried to climb down\Nthe veranda in that costume
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:05.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to scare the attendee\Nin the room below.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.76,0:07:09.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But he screwed up\Nand fell to his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:10.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:13.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the 21st floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:16.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Would he really try to\Ngo down without a rope?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:19.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, the key was inside the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:24.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If he did make it to the room\Nbelow and then left through it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:27.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he would've needed the\Nkey to get back in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.90,0:07:29.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:34.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My pen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:37.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let me have\Na look at the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:39.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:42.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing it won't\Nchange anything, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:49.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:55.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So he fell 21 stories\Nonto that statue...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:57.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Has anyone gotten near the body?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.56,0:08:02.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, sir. Aside from us, only one\Nother person has touched him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.35,0:08:03.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That little boy there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:07.09,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That brat again!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.11,0:08:13.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:17.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find the pen\Nthat I dropped...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:22.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that Ebara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was\Nthe one who fell, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:25.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No question about it.\NIt was Tokio Ebara.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:28.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And he had a mask on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:30.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A mask!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:37.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So he was the tour\Norganiser and the Night Baron.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:41.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it. I always\Nthought he was suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:43.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off. This isn't the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:49.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it is disturbing that the\Nimmortal Night Baron would perish...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:51.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.95,0:08:54.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Members of the same tour I'm on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:56.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But why would Ebara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:08:59.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:00.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,An accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:04.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He fell off the veranda\Ntrying to scare you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:10.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate,\Nthe Night Baron has died.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.05,0:09:12.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the tour is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:17.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:21.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Weird. What's with this necktie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:24.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the knot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:27.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The knot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:30.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's backwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:32.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But this could be normal for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:35.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a necktie of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:36.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:39.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you get that necktie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.74,0:09:42.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A waitress gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:44.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She said he forgot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:47.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true! This tie's knot is normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:48.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, re, re!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:50.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh!? Is there something else!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:53.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's wearing his belt weird, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:09:55.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See? It's upside-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:58.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not good with\Naccessories, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:10:01.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is very strange, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:04.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He didn't put these clothes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:06.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone put them on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:10.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means Ebara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was\Npushed off the 21st floor
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:13.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,by the real Night Baron.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:18.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the homicidal\NNight Baron is still among us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:27.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears we must ask\Nwhere each of you were
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.42,0:10:30.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,when Ebara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} fell at 10 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:34.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.81,0:10:34.77,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Interrogation Room
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.81,0:10:34.77,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuoka Police
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.81,0:10:34.77,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Authorised Personnel Only
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.77,0:10:39.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, at 10 PM you were in the observation\Nlounge with Ran and Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.24,0:10:43.12,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru Maeda (30)\NJōnan University Electrical Engineering Assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.24,0:10:44.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0010,,Yes. I left them some time after 10 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.24,0:10:46.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:50.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But y{\i1}ou{\i} were the one who\Nlooked at the time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:52.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:55.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. Call in the next person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:11:00.43,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideko Kamijō (29) -\NSoftware Company CEO
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:58.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0020,,My alibi's airtight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.53,0:11:04.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0020,,Since I was in the pub with him the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:05.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Mr. Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:07.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:12.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But didn't he get dead-drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.34,0:11:14.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.92,0:11:16.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:19.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0040,,We were in an open-air restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.43,0:11:21.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0040,,near where Ebara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:21.20,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen'ichirō Kaneshiro (74)\NComputer Company Owner
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:24.87,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizue Hayashi (56)\NKaneshiro's Butler
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:23.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0040,,Isn't that right, Shizue{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.31,0:11:24.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0040,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.97,0:11:27.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can anyone vouch for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:34.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was such a commotion that\NI'm unsure people would remember us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:39.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But with the way he died,\NI can't say I blame them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:42.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring in the next one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:49.89,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirō Kon'no (28)\NBank Employee
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.88,0:11:47.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in my room reading my e-mail
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.16,0:11:50.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,from 9:45 until after 10 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:54.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The hotel's records should prove that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.17,0:11:57.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you didn't speak\Nwith anyone, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:12:01.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I did. With my computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:03.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.51,0:12:05.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Call in the next person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:08.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were alone in your room, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:12.08,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko Sayama (24)\NHigh School Math Teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.27,0:12:09.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0040,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:12.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0040,,I was watching TV alone
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:14.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0040,,until Satoru returned after 10 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:18.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I take it you have\Nnobody to vouch for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:21.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can describe what the\Nmovie was about, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.36,0:12:23.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a bomb in a skyscraper...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.07,0:12:27.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. That won't work as proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:36.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe they\Nmade me guard him alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:39.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they finish\Ntheir questioning soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:44.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That detective and your\Nfather really tick me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.09,0:12:46.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet they think I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:48.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.56,0:12:51.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's tons of other\Nsuspicious people!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.49,0:12:52.39,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10\fad(0,500)}Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:56.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is my shift over?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.96,0:12:59.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.61,0:13:06.18,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Everyone on the tour\Nhas a flimsy alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:10.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you maybe order room service\Nwhen you were in your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.66,0:13:13.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've already said so if I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:19.52,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}How did the killer leave after\Npushing Ebara{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} off his veranda?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:23.55,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The room had its security lock set!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:29.89,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}All we know is that the\Nkiller is still in the hotel...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:32.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You called the front desk!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:35.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I asked for a wake-up call.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:36.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When was that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:39.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,About 10 PM, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:43.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The hotel keeps records of\Nwhen calls are made from rooms!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:47.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That means your alibi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:50.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Akiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.06,0:13:58.88,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10\fad(200,200)}The Night Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:06.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Night Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:09.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:11.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:25.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.34,0:14:28.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing!?\NHe's getting away! Ran-{\i1}néechan{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:30.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran-{\i1}néechan{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:32.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What!? He showed up!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:35.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the heck didn't you catch him!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:37.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I was in shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.67,0:14:39.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Yokomizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.64,0:14:40.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.63,0:14:42.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was collapsed in the\Nroom with the body!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.96,0:14:45.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears he was hit by someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:47.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh!? And the body!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:51.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, but the Night\NBaron costume is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:53.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Night Baron costume!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.31,0:14:54.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:55.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Yokomizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:56.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:58.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Night Baron's in the pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:14:58.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.62,0:15:04.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The mask, hat, wig, and cape!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:07.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So what about the one wearing it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.99,0:15:09.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where could he or she be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:14.01,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Probably up there.\NIt was tossed from that balcony.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:17.52,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Why did the killer show\Nup at the elevators{\i}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:21.46,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}If they needed to go up, they would've\Nused the stairs to go unseen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:25.21,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}And why did they have\Nto wear the costume,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.21,0:15:28.11,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}not to mention risk being\Ncaught trying to steal it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:30.14,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His methods are too aggressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.14,0:15:33.43,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Could these latest things\Nhave been unplanned!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:36.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! We need to re-question them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:38.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Round up all the suspects!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:39.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:44.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were all in your rooms,\Nand you have no witnesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:46.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means none of you\Nhave alibis for when
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:49.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and the others\Nwere attacked! Correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.91,0:15:52.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:57.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You told us not to leave our rooms,\Nand that's just what we did!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.83,0:16:00.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We only did as you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.83,0:16:04.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not stupid enough\Nto ignore the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.29,0:16:06.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.02,0:16:08.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Maeda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nshare the same room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:11.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't check if\Nthey were there or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:12.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There was no time to!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:17.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We all came right away to\Nreport about the Night Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:17.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:19.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:23.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, we'll need\Nto check all your rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.69,0:16:26.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yours first, Maeda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.11,0:16:26.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:34.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing seems out of the ordinary...\NWhat the...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:35.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.95,0:16:37.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just letting some air in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:41.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That stupid kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:44.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just to be sure,\Nplease empty your pockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:47.31,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I have this room's\Nlayout figured out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.31,0:16:50.78,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Ebara{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} fell\Nfrom that veranda...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:55.22,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Yes. The killer dressed\Nhim up as the Night Baron
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.22,0:16:59.20,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and pushed him off to make\Nit look like an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:03.04,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But the security lock was set\Nin the room where it happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:08.29,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}In other words, the killer didn't\Nleave through the door afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:11.13,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Meaning this was a locked-room murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:15.66,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The veranda is the only other way out of the room...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.66,0:17:19.14,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But going from there into\Nthis room is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:21.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's this medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:23.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ordinary sleeping pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:26.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I always carry them with me for\Nmy insomnia. That a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:29.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I see?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:31.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go to the next room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.59,0:17:36.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't find anything, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:39.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just making sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.56,0:17:42.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Him again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:46.15,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The veranda he fell from\Nis directly above...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.15,0:17:48.42,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It might be possible\Nto climb down here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:50.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you keep following me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.53,0:17:54.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd watch your great\Ndetective skills in action!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.45,0:17:58.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay! In that case,\Npay close attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:01.29,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}There are no signs of\Nthe window being broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.29,0:18:03.75,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Guess he can be cute sometimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:06.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Was this window always locked, Mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.63,0:18:12.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes are bad.\NCan you answer, Shizue{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.30,0:18:16.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it was. I check\Nit each time we leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:18.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kon'no{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s room is next.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:24.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that he was suspected\Nof using his bank's computers
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.85,0:18:27.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,without permission\Nand was thus demoted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:31.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He may have wanted to see\Nthe Baron the most of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.98,0:18:32.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.98,0:18:35.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's simply a rumor, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:38.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that old man told you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:39.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:44.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's he to talk? He's the one who\Nhates the Night Baron the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.79,0:18:46.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:52.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, the son he so dutifully\Nraised was murdered by the virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:56.17,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Come to think of it,\Nhe did mention that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:18:59.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Night Baron. Hearing that\Nname brings back memories
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:03.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,of my son who died four years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:05.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A virus? His son died of an illness?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.64,0:19:08.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that have to do\Nwith the Night Baron!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.19,0:19:10.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good question...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:11.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you playing dumb!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:13.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:17.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop! I'll give you\Nsome special information!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:21.49,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This is the closest window to the veranda,\Nbut there's no way across.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.49,0:19:23.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With Kamijō{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.29,0:19:26.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They were married.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:29.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I hear they\Ndivorced three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:34.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. The late\NTokio Ebara was my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.63,0:19:39.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was three years ago...\Nwhen I learned he was a hacker.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:40.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hacker?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:44.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A criminal who steals computer data!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:48.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who uses a\Ncomputer loathes hackers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.48,0:19:53.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm relieved that he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:54.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.23,0:19:59.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe Akiko Sayama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s brother\Nran a small software company.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:03.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means she's no exception, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:08.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning that everyone on the\Ntour had a reason to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:10.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.73,0:20:15.71,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh? These are the same\Npills that Akiko{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} {\i0}had...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.71,0:20:17.51,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Are these also{\i}-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:20.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, what are these pills for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.13,0:20:23.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't touch my things!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.51,0:20:25.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it cold medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.14,0:20:26.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-yes, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:29.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I thought they were\Nsleeping pills. Guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.44,0:20:31.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.54,0:20:37.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you blabbing about now!?\NGo get in bed, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.92,0:20:40.84,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I didn't check the room's layout yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.01,0:20:47.62,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Ah, well. It's the same layout\Nas Kon'no{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s room downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:51.64,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Well, looking at\Neveryone's rooms, we get...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.10,0:20:58.61,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Room 2101\NEbara
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.85,0:20:58.61,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Room 2102\NKamijō
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.85,0:20:58.61,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Room 2001\NKaneshiro, Hayashi
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:58.61,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Room 2002\NKon'no
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:58.61,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Room 1901\NMaeda, Sayama
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:58.61,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Body
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:20:58.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...as a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.65,0:21:01.93,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}So the only possible escape\Nfrom Ebara{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s veranda
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.93,0:21:04.43,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}was through Kaneshiro{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}\N{\i0}and Hayashi{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s room...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:05.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do we do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:09.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure. It's a piece\Nof the security lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:12.66,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh, right. Ebara{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s room\Nis on this floor, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:15.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there's something on the tip...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.16,0:21:16.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cellophane tape!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:20.78,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Wait a minute! Could this be{\i}-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.11,0:21:27.13,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He dodged all of my kicks\Nwith no effort at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.13,0:21:35.14,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}And only one of the suspects could've done that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:37.10,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What should I do!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.10,0:21:40.13,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Tell me, Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.13,0:21:42.07,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:46.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Open up, Ran-{\i1}néechan{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:48.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.72,0:21:50.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The security lock was set.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.81,0:21:54.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange. I don't\Nremember locking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.27,0:21:55.56,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Success!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.56,0:21:57.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.42,0:22:00.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Some tears came out when I yawned.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.54,0:22:03.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm leaving for a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.38,0:22:04.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This late!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.11,0:22:05.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.59,0:22:08.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.88,0:22:11.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kids shouldn't be awake this late.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.35,0:22:13.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.18,0:22:16.63,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Using that trick, anyone\Ncould have killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.63,0:22:19.09,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'll have to check\Neach of their alibis...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.09,0:22:21.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you hear about Misawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.71,0:22:25.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,About how the killer knocked him\Nout in the office with the body?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.03,0:22:27.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't Misawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} a karate expert?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.99,0:22:30.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Best in the department!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.87,0:22:34.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he {\i1}was{\i} caught off guard...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.06,0:22:35.91,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Hey, hey, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.91,0:22:38.61,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10\fad(0,300)}Could the killer be...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.08,0:24:06.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I locked it from the outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.09,0:24:09.00,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What would Shin'ichi do in this situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.00,0:24:11.05,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's the pen I dropped...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.05,0:24:12.63,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Not surprising...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.63,0:24:15.59,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It {\i1}did{\i0} fall from Ebara{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s room on the 21st floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.59,0:24:16.60,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.60,0:24:19.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Now I know who did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.06,0:24:23.52,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I can't believe I didn't realise something this simple...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.52,0:24:27.44,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Now I'm sure! That's the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.44,0:24:33.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0040,,On the next Conan: "The Night Baron Murder Case (Case Closed)"
